  <entry>
    <title>主题配置</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/01/21/%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/01/21/%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</id>
    <published>2022-01-21T12:28:14.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-01-21T15:17:40.352Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="配置文件说明"><a href="#配置文件说明" class="headerlink" title="配置文件说明"></a>配置文件说明</h2><p>主题配置文件 <code>_config.yml</code> 是 hexo 主题内的配置文件。</p><blockquote><p>AAA/themes/XXX</p><p>AAA代指博客主目录</p><p>XXX代指主题名</p></blockquote><span id="more"></span><h2 id="语言"><a href="#语言" class="headerlink" title="语言"></a>语言</h2><blockquote><p>该项修改须在博客主目录下的 <code>_config.yml</code> 修改</p></blockquote><p>选项：default(en) / en / zh-hans</p><h2 id="自定义主题色"><a href="#自定义主题色" class="headerlink" title="自定义主题色"></a>自定义主题色</h2><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">theme_color:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment"># or false -&gt; to use the default theme</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">main:</span> <span class="string">&quot;#282828&quot;</span> <span class="comment">#主题颜色</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">paginator:</span> <span class="string">&quot;#000&quot;</span> <span class="comment"># 侧边栏</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">button_hover:</span> <span class="string">&quot;#49B1F5&quot;</span> <span class="comment"># 移动收到无序列表上</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">text_selection:</span> <span class="string">&quot;#3a96dd&quot;</span> <span class="comment"># 文字选中后 </span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">link_color:</span> <span class="string">&quot;#000&quot;</span> <span class="comment"># 链接颜色</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">hr_color:</span> <span class="string">&quot;#646464&quot;</span> <span class="comment"># 分割线颜色</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">meta_color:</span> <span class="string">&quot;#000&quot;</span> <span class="comment"># 顶部导航栏阴影色</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">header_text_color:</span> <span class="string">&quot;#fff&quot;</span> <span class="comment"># v1.7.0+ 头部文本颜色</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">footer_text_color:</span> <span class="string">&quot;#fff&quot;</span> <span class="comment"># v1.7.0+ 底部文本颜色</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p><font color=red>注意</font>：颜色值必须被双引号包裹，就像<code>&quot;#000&quot;</code>而不是<code>#000</code>。否则将会在构建的时候报错！</p></blockquote><h2 id="代码高亮主题"><a href="#代码高亮主题" class="headerlink" title="代码高亮主题"></a>代码高亮主题</h2><p><code>theme-melody</code> 支持如下几种代码高亮样式：</p><ul><li>default</li><li>darker</li><li>pale night</li><li>light</li></ul><h2 id="代码换行"><a href="#代码换行" class="headerlink" title="代码换行"></a>代码换行</h2><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">code_word_wrap:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后在博客目录下的<code>_config.yml</code> 修改 <code>line_number</code> 为false</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">highlight:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">line_number:</span> <span class="literal">false</span> <span class="comment"># &lt;- 改这里</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">auto_detect:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">tab_replace:</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后重新部署并启动</p><h2 id="导航菜单"><a href="#导航菜单" class="headerlink" title="导航菜单"></a>导航菜单</h2><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 导航菜单</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">menu:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">主页:</span> <span class="string">/#</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">存档:</span> <span class="string">/archives</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">标签:</span> <span class="string">/tags</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">分类:</span> <span class="string">/categories</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>创建tags和categories页面请看上一篇文章《设置标签和分类》</p><h2 id="顶部图"><a href="#顶部图" class="headerlink" title="顶部图"></a>顶部图</h2><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 顶部图，true/false/link</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">top_img:</span> <span class="string">/img/eyw528.png</span> <span class="comment"># 可以是true（开启，默认的图片）、false（关闭）、</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 顶部图高度控制 60 - 100</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">top_img_height:</span> <span class="number">100</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="为特定的文章页配置特定的顶部图"><a href="#为特定的文章页配置特定的顶部图" class="headerlink" title="为特定的文章页配置特定的顶部图"></a>为特定的文章页配置特定的顶部图</h3><p>在md文件头部加入 <code>top_img</code> </p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">Hi,</span> <span class="string">theme-melody!</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">tags:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">top_img:</span> <span class="string">https://xxxxxxx.jpg</span>   <span class="comment"># &lt; top_img在这里插入，同样可以使用本地路径</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="number">2017-09-07</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果有特定文章顶部图，全局的顶部图不会显示</p><blockquote><p>图片的存放位置为主题目录下的 <code>source/img</code> 目录中</p></blockquote><h2 id="文章相关项"><a href="#文章相关项" class="headerlink" title="文章相关项"></a>文章相关项</h2><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">post_meta:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">date_type:</span> <span class="string">created</span> <span class="comment"># or updated 文章日期是创建日或者更新日</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">categories:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment"># or false 是否显示分类</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">tags:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment"># or false 是否显示标签</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="文章版权"><a href="#文章版权" class="headerlink" title="文章版权"></a>文章版权</h2><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">post_copyright:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">license:</span> <span class="string">CC</span> <span class="string">BY-NC-SA</span> <span class="number">3.0</span> <span class="comment"># 协议名称</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">license_url:</span> <span class="string">https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/</span> <span class="comment"># 协议说明地址</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="文章相关二维码"><a href="#文章相关二维码" class="headerlink" title="文章相关二维码"></a>文章相关二维码</h2><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">QR_code:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">itemlist:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">img:</span> <span class="string">https://xxxx1.jpg</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">text:</span> <span class="string">支付宝打赏</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">itemlist:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">img:</span> <span class="string">https://xxxx2.jpg</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">text:</span> <span class="string">微信打赏</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>文章结尾的打赏用</p><blockquote><p>图片的存放位置为主题目录下的 <code>source/img</code> 目录中</p></blockquote><h2 id="侧边栏展示控制"><a href="#侧边栏展示控制" class="headerlink" title="侧边栏展示控制"></a>侧边栏展示控制</h2><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">idebar_display:</span> <span class="string">post</span> <span class="comment"># all/index/post/index-none/post-none/hidden</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><code>all</code>: 所有的页面都会自动展示侧边栏</li><li><code>index</code>: 只有首页会自动展示侧边栏</li><li><code>post</code>: 只有文章页会自动展示侧边栏</li><li><code>index-none</code>: 只有首页不会自动展示侧边栏</li><li><code>post-none</code>: 只有文章页不会自动展示侧边栏</li><li><code>hidden</code>: 所有的页面都不会自动展示侧边栏</li></ul><h2 id="头像"><a href="#头像" class="headerlink" title="头像"></a>头像</h2><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">avatar:</span> <span class="string">https://xxxx.jpg</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>可用网络图或本地图</p></blockquote><blockquote><p>如使用本地图片，图片的存放位置为主题目录下的 <code>source/img</code> 目录中</p></blockquote><h2 id="Follow-Me按钮（人太垃圾了，没有设置）"><a href="#Follow-Me按钮（人太垃圾了，没有设置）" class="headerlink" title="Follow Me按钮（人太垃圾了，没有设置）"></a>Follow Me按钮（人太垃圾了，没有设置）</h2><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">follow:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">url:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;https://github.com/USERNAME&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">text:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Follow Me&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="友链"><a href="#友链" class="headerlink" title="友链"></a>友链</h2><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">links_title:</span> <span class="string">Links</span>   <span class="comment"># 配置友链的标题文字</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">links:</span></span><br><span class="line"> [<span class="string">页面中显示的名称</span>]<span class="string">:</span> [<span class="string">链接</span>] <span class="comment"># 名称：URL</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="目录"><a href="#目录" class="headerlink" title="目录"></a>目录</h2><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">toc:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment"># or false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">number:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment"># or false. 版本v1.5.6新增</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="博客年份"><a href="#博客年份" class="headerlink" title="博客年份"></a>博客年份</h2><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">since:</span> <span class="number">2013</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>展示站点创建时间的选项，在底部</p><h2 id="页脚自定义文本"><a href="#页脚自定义文本" class="headerlink" title="页脚自定义文本"></a>页脚自定义文本</h2><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">footer_custom_text:</span> <span class="string">Hi,</span> <span class="string">welcome</span> <span class="string">to</span> <span class="string">my</span> <span class="string">blog!</span> <span class="comment"># 自定义的文本或 hitokoto：生成随机的谚语</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>可使用html标记，不推荐使用复杂的标记</p></blockquote><h2 id="特效"><a href="#特效" class="headerlink" title="特效"></a>特效</h2><h3 id="烟花"><a href="#烟花" class="headerlink" title="烟花"></a>烟花</h3><p>模仿<a href="http://animejs.com/">anime.js官网</a>的点击效果</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">fireworks:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="彩带（不推荐使用，卡顿严重，不丝滑）"><a href="#彩带（不推荐使用，卡顿严重，不丝滑）" class="headerlink" title="彩带（不推荐使用，卡顿严重，不丝滑）"></a>彩带（不推荐使用，卡顿严重，不丝滑）</h3><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">canvas_ribbon:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">size:</span> <span class="number">150</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">alpha:</span> <span class="number">0.6</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">zIndex:</span> <span class="number">-1</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">click_to_change:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="字数统计"><a href="#字数统计" class="headerlink" title="字数统计"></a>字数统计</h2><ol><li>打开 hexo 工作目录</li><li><code>npm install hexo-wordcount --save</code> or <code>yarn add hexo-wordcount</code></li><li>配置<code>melody.yml</code></li></ol><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">wordcount:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>找到 <code>themes/melody/layout</code> ,打开 <code>post.pug</code> 推荐使用Sublime Text或VSCode打开，可以看到代码高亮。</p><p>搜索<code>.post-meta-wordcount</code> 修改下面的代码</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* 修改前 */</span></span><br><span class="line">span=_P(<span class="string">&#x27;post.wordcount&#x27;</span>)+<span class="string">&#x27;: &#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">span.word-count= wordcount(page.content)</span><br><span class="line">span.post-meta__separator |</span><br><span class="line">span=_P(<span class="string">&#x27;post.min2read&#x27;</span>,min2read(page.count,&#123;<span class="attr">cn</span>: <span class="number">350</span>,<span class="attr">en</span>: <span class="number">160</span>&#125;)) </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* 修改后 */</span></span><br><span class="line">span=<span class="string">&#x27;字数统计: &#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">span.word-count= wordcount(page.content)+<span class="string">&#x27;字&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">span.post-meta__separator |</span><br><span class="line">span= <span class="string">&quot;阅读时长约 &quot;</span>+_p( min2read(page.content, &#123;<span class="attr">cn</span>: <span class="number">350</span>, <span class="attr">en</span>: <span class="number">160</span>&#125;))+<span class="string">&#x27;分钟&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">cn是指一分钟能阅读的中文字数</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">en是指一分钟能阅读的英文字叔</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">*/</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="文章置顶"><a href="#文章置顶" class="headerlink" title="文章置顶"></a>文章置顶</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: xxxx</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line">date: 2018-08-08 08:08:08</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">top: True # 设置top属性，并置为true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;h2 id=&quot;配置文件说明&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#配置文件说明&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;配置文件说明&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;配置文件说明&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;主题配置文件 &lt;code&gt;_config.yml&lt;/code&gt; 是 hexo 主题内的配置文件。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;AAA/themes/XXX&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;AAA代指博客主目录&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;XXX代指主题名&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
