  <entry>
    <title>设置标签和分类</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/01/21/%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E5%92%8C%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/01/21/%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E5%92%8C%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB/</id>
    <published>2022-01-21T08:00:10.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-01-21T15:17:04.106Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ul><li><p>创建“分类”</p><ol><li><p>打开博客所在文件夹，并执行命令</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> hexo new page categories</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>成功后提示</p><p><code>INFO  Created: F:\hexo\Blog\source\categories\index.md</code></p><blockquote><p>F:\hexo\Blog\  是我存放hexo博客的根目录</p></blockquote><span id="more"></span></li><li><p>打开上述路径的index.md文件，打开后</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: categories</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">date: 2022-01-21 16:00:00</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>添加<code>type: categories</code>到内容中</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: categories</span><br><span class="line">date: 2022-01-21 16:00:00</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">type: categories</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p> hexo一篇文章只能属于一个分类</p><p>如果在“AAA”下方添加“BBB”，hexo不会产生两个分类，而是把分类嵌套（即该文章属于 “AAA”下的 “BBB”分类）</p></blockquote></li></ol></li><li><p>创建标签</p><ol><li><p>打开博客所在文件夹，并执行命令</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> hexo new page tags</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>成功后提示</p><p><code>INFO  Created: F:\hexo\Blog\source\categories\index.md</code></p><blockquote><p>F:\hexo\Blog\  是我存放hexo博客的根目录</p></blockquote></li><li><p>打开上述路径的index.md文件，打开后</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: tags</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">date: 2022-01-21 16:00:00</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>添加<code>type: categories</code>到内容中</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: tags</span><br><span class="line">date: 2022-01-21 16:00:00</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">type: tags</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>hexo一篇文章可以有多个标签</p><p>在tags下添加多个名称会创建多个标签</p></blockquote></li></ol></li></ul><hr><p>为特定的文章添加顶部图</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: Hi, theme-melody!</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line">top<span class="emphasis">_img: https://xxxxxxx.jpg   # &lt; top_</span>img在这里插入</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section"># 或从public目录中依次填写本地路径</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">date: 2022-01-21</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;创建“分类”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;打开博客所在文件夹，并执行命令&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight shell&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;meta&quot;&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;bash&quot;&gt; hexo new page categories&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;成功后提示&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;INFO  Created: F:\hexo\Blog\source\categories\index.md&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;F:\hexo\Blog\  是我存放hexo博客的根目录&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
